  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/ec5588d5c839103b698ff90dbc85aeaf.avif?t=1773774325\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Mini Putt is a multiplayer minigolf game for you and your friends! Enjoy our carefully crafted maps and maps made by our awesome community using our advanced map editor! No, we will not charge for new maps, outfits, hats or anything!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>16 Player Multiplayer</strong> <br>Invite up to 16 of your friends into a game of Mini Putt to show of your skills.<br><br><strong>Ball Customisations</strong><br>Unlock balls, faces, hats and trails to stand out from the other putters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.poster.avif?t=1773774325\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.webm?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.mp4?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Advanced Map Editor</strong><br>Create your own awesome maps and share them with other putters.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Terrain Editor<br></li><li> 100s of unique models<br></li><li> Awesome model components</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/6b5f42dfd1481e11dd12fdbeafd09403.poster.avif?t=1773774325\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/6b5f42dfd1481e11dd12fdbeafd09403.webm?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Free DLC</strong><br>We will not charge for any additional content that we add to Mini Putt, we want the game to be as fun as possible for everyone!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/ec5588d5c839103b698ff90dbc85aeaf.avif?t=1773774325\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Mini Putt is a multiplayer minigolf game for you and your friends! Enjoy our carefully crafted maps and maps made by our awesome community using our advanced map editor! No, we will not charge for new maps, outfits, hats or anything!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>16 Player Multiplayer</strong> <br>Invite up to 16 of your friends into a game of Mini Putt to show of your skills.<br><br><strong>Ball Customisations</strong><br>Unlock balls, faces, hats and trails to stand out from the other putters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.poster.avif?t=1773774325\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.webm?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/c484722d5f0cc172df420a75e00dcf8b.mp4?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Advanced Map Editor</strong><br>Create your own awesome maps and share them with other putters.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Terrain Editor<br></li><li> 100s of unique models<br></li><li> Awesome model components</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/6b5f42dfd1481e11dd12fdbeafd09403.poster.avif?t=1773774325\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965260/extras/6b5f42dfd1481e11dd12fdbeafd09403.webm?t=1773774325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Free DLC</strong><br>We will not charge for any additional content that we add to Mini Putt, we want the game to be as fun as possible for everyone!",
